    Mauro Di Girolamo

    • Field Summary

      private int alignmentEnd

      • isCircular

        public boolean isCircular()
        Checks whether the Read is circular and returns this information as a boolean.

        Take a look at the CircularParser.constructCircularRead(main.model.Read, htsjdk.samtools.SAMRecord, boolean) method to get a better understanding of why this check does the desired.

        Returns:
        true if the Read is circular, false otherwise
